      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s the proper syntax for offsetof. The macro you were using actually expanded to this, in context.\n\nThe only reason for the \u0026 is to force expansion of a macro argument that otherwise wouldn\u0027t expand. (See: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/assembler/masm/operator-logical-and-masm?view\u003dvs-2019)",
